00:47:20,920 --> 00:47:23,115
Sorry I can't stick around
for the smoothie.

705
00:47:23,280 --> 00:47:25,748
You don't know everything
there is to know.

706
00:47:25,920 --> 00:47:29,959
No, like some things never get old,
and, um... My car is here.

707
00:47:30,120 --> 00:47:34,159
Look, this time, you're
really wrong, Emma. You are.

708
00:47:36,840 --> 00:47:39,559
Goodbye, Wilder.

709
00:47:39,720 --> 00:47:41,915
