papers and we'll put this behind us.

722
00:48:29,680 --> 00:48:31,830
Um, well...

723
00:48:35,280 --> 00:48:36,599
I don't have the papers.

724
00:48:38,760 --> 00:48:40,910
- What's going on, Em?
- I don't know.

725
00:48:41,080 --> 00:48:44,595
He had them at the book signing.
Between the dinner and the upanayanam...

726
00:48:44,760 --> 00:48:48,992
Indian bar mitzvah, don't ask,
I misplaced them.

727
00:48:49,160 --> 00:48:51,355
- I had them in my hands!
- Don't worry about it.

728
00:48:51,520 --> 00:48:54,557
- It's so unlike me.
- It's all right.

729
00:48:54,720 --> 00:48:57,154
I'm gonna take care of everything
from now on.

730
00:48:59,720 --> 00:49:02,757
A white lie is still a lie.
