00:49:12,120 --> 00:49:15,795
will erode the foundation
of your relationship.

735
00:49:15,960 --> 00:49:20,112
- You're getting married soon, right?
- Yep. That's right.

736
00:49:20,280 --> 00:49:24,398
Your fiancé must be a lucky man
to know he has you to keep him honest.

737
00:49:24,560 --> 00:49:26,073
We're both very lucky.

738
00:49:26,240 --> 00:49:29,550
Brother Carl.
Didn't know you played.

739
00:49:29,720 --> 00:49:33,156
Let's drop the bullshit, shall we?
It's Richard.

740
00:49:33,320 --> 00:49:37,108
- Richard Braxton, as you well know.
- Patrick Sullivan, as you well know.

741
00:49:37,280 --> 00:49:39,999
Hell, we're practically family.

