744
00:49:45,800 --> 00:49:48,712
- And I appreciate that.
- It was fun.

745
00:49:48,880 --> 00:49:51,713
I have to play the spoil-sport
and ask for those papers.

746
00:49:51,880 --> 00:49:54,758
- So we can go separate ways.
- I'll bring them by the office.

747
00:49:54,920 --> 00:49:57,309
- No, that's not gonna happen.
- Why's that?

748
00:49:57,480 --> 00:49:59,755
She and I have a life
which doesn't include you...

