00:52:29,760 --> 00:52:32,115
Instead of blaming others
for your problems...

782
00:52:32,280 --> 00:52:35,511
- Consider looking at yourself.
- I'm looking right at my problem.

783
00:52:35,680 --> 00:52:41,630
- Well, stop fogging up the mirror.
- Nice.

784
00:52:41,800 --> 00:52:45,759
- Did you just hang up on a caller?
