talk you into marrying me.

854
00:58:42,200 --> 00:58:44,668
Take a few days
and figure out what it is you want.

855
00:58:44,840 --> 00:58:47,559
In fact, why don't we
begin that right now.

856
00:58:47,720 --> 00:58:49,631
Richard.

857
00:58:51,400 --> 00:58:55,393
We had a really
nice time. Good conversation.

858
00:58:55,560 --> 00:58:58,632
He was sweet and funny,
but I don't know. Something's missing.

859
00:58:58,800 --> 00:59:01,633
- There was no... Exactly.
