866
00:59:32,040 --> 00:59:36,477
Actually, his girlfriend's daughter
is wearing your robe.

867
00:59:36,640 --> 00:59:39,518
- Hello, Emma.
- Aren't you my?...

868
00:59:41,200 --> 00:59:44,715
So, um, why the big secret?

869
00:59:44,880 --> 00:59:47,952
I wanted to tell you.
