01:00:09,200 --> 01:00:11,794
...on this introduction
until we were sure of each other.

877
01:00:11,960 --> 01:00:14,633
- And are we?
- Well, I am.

878
01:00:14,800 --> 01:00:19,351
I can't even keep track of all
the things I've misunderstood.

879
01:00:19,520 --> 01:00:20,839
Sorry.

880
