882
01:00:31,480 --> 01:00:36,634
Well, sure, honey. What's not to like?
I mean, he's perfect, isn't he?

883
01:00:36,800 --> 01:00:40,349
- Is that a compliment?
- You don't need compliments from me.

884
01:00:40,520 --> 01:00:43,034
I've never told you
how to live or who to date.

885
01:00:43,200 --> 01:00:46,192
